{"tid":1538352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察咁樣對你哋，你哋袋住先？","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:42:51.000Z","uid":252007,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea49a87c0880d1877ace826d22336edbf442a4e","tid":1538352,"uid":252007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"攰喇，想唞吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都搞咗咁耐，政府都回應咗啦，算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我DNLM啦！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">612<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">八個義士、成千個被捕手足，仲三個下落下明嘅手足！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一日未爭取到，一日都要戰鬥落去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">五大訴求，決一不可</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"29c15b1a290bd51ce7d3303259d4e2fc5001d03f","tid":1538352,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:54:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0ae82c3ffa2ad7a9ffeee654ab12c5880456b63","tid":1538352,"uid":11277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab83a3cd608c308ce457e8e9a9e2c660fc073695","tid":1538352,"uid":40328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04