ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2c1409bd646548e16fc69aa2c3436f1085b34b7","tid":1538352,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"千萬計被打被害既義士手足<br />\n無故被斬被打既乘客<br />\n失眼以至身體永久創傷既港人<br />\n被迫吸有毒氣體既市民<br />\n盡道而死既英雄<br />\n未FC被打死被姦既烈士<br />\n12歲上街既小朋友<br />\n學校被捉血流滿面既學生<br />\n<br />\n仲有我地大家香港人<br />\n<br />\n今次政府已經挑起不可收拾的局面<br />\n拒絕袋住先，妥協<br />\n必須正視警暴問題，冇可能可以平息<br />\n當我地已經揸住暴政春袋就要起勢扯<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會放棄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家copy and paste"},{"pid":"be32cac56647211e202bba8bfb0d15b9098901b3","tid":1538352,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JOND7u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JOND7u.png&h=55097fe2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4705710829cfe717213e95dac60e4222256a1f4","tid":1538352,"uid":252007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求 決一不可</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41124b1a472c7dbeed25c3125917c6a324a6a6bd","tid":1538352,"uid":252007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求 決一不可</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f827cb28621dd3075a50fab8abaf417b21528d","tid":1538352